## Usage Pattern
Replace AI API base URLs with Netlify deployment URL:
- `https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com` → `https://your-site.netlify.app/gemini`
- `https://api.anthropic.com` → `https://your-site.netlify.app/claude`
- `https://api.openai.com` → `https://your-site.netlify.app/openai`

